---
title: Sesame Beef & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Spice up your night (and your tastebuds!) with this speedy stir-fry sensation that's sure to delight all the hungry eaters. Tender beef coated in a sesame-soy marinade is the star of the show, supported by an array of colourful veggies and a smattering of crispy shallots, the bowls are sure to be empty in minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-beef-broccoli-stir-fry-97f77013.jpg
